question: Which user is logging into the VPN from the city Benicia on 9/18/2020?
how_to_solve:
If you want the non-tstats SPL for it:  
index="firewall" sourcetype="pan:system" 
| iplocation src_ip 
| stats values(user) by City
Answer Logic: Visual inspection of Global Protect VPN Login Activities dashboard
hint1: Is there a dashboard panel for Global Protect VPN Logins by City?
hint2: Did you scroll to the bottom?
